{"tid":2163112,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣封殺愛奇藝、騰訊！經濟部出手 9/3 全面禁止中國 OTT","createTime":"2020-08-18T12:58:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T14:21:53.000Z","uid":199772,"like":66,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b43ed3b6c16dd9fe72174fea7cb5e2993f2346b0","tid":2163112,"uid":199772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:58:51.000Z","msg":"//<span class=\"orange\">為防止愛奇藝以及騰訊等大陸地區OTT（Over-The-Top）TV服務到台</span>，台灣經濟部正式預告「在台灣地區從事商業行為禁止事項項目表」，將代理或經銷大陸OTT及相關商業服務納入禁止範圍，預告期滿後，將於9月3日正式生效。//<br />\n<br />\n//台灣經濟部指出，<span class=\"orange\">OTT TV服務並非開放陸資投資項目，在政治、社會、文化上具有敏感性或影響國家安全之虞</span>，禁止事項項目表修正後，預告期為14天，會聽取各界意見與看法，預計於9月1日期滿，9月3日公告實施。//<br />\n<br />\n//經濟部官員表示，推動修法主要是因<span class=\"orange\">兩岸審查機制不對等，台灣的環境相對自由</span>，加上兩岸條例並未將OTT列為陸資可投資項目，為防範陸資繞很多彎到台灣落地，才進行修法。//<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全文見:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200818/QMQFPKZHIBE6ZBWIQJYAKVAAJI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200818%2FQMQFPKZHIBE6ZBWIQJYAKVAAJI%2F&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5hTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=0d6fd557\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200818%2FQMQFPKZHIBE6ZBWIQJYAKVAAJI%2F&h=091cf4e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200818/QMQFPKZHIBE6ZBWIQJYAKVAAJI/</a>"},{"pid":"11de349b98ce6024d98405d7302246431c79bb8e","tid":2163112,"uid":54502,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T13:01:23.000Z","msg":"等巴哈碼特買多d動畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b5a064bd8797bca89a0b2ab72ec60ce5dc5ff4f","tid":2163112,"uid":199772,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T13:06:54.000Z","msg":"無得再走法律罅<br />\n陸資請返大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" c